    <item>
      <title>de minimus关税漏洞特朗普关闭了什么？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/de-minimis-why-trump-ended-tariff-loophole-used-by-shein-temu</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一个曾经在海关经纪人世界以外鲜为人知的拉丁语术语已成为头条新闻。这要归功于美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）于4月2日签署了一项行政命令，以关闭来自中国和香港的“ de Minimis”商品的关税漏洞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/de-minimis-why-trump-ended-tariff-loophole-used-by-shein-temu</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 15:39:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的第二任期带来了自2001年以来最糟糕的股市开始</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-s-second-term-brings-worst-stock-market-start-since-2001</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自从唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）就职典礼以来，美国股票市场几乎下跌了10％，这标志着自2001年乔治·W·布什（George W. Bush）自2001年在Dot-Com抛售期间的新总统以来的最糟糕的开局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-s-second-term-brings-worst-stock-market-start-since-2001</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 15:32:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当关税战争激发了增长恐惧时，美国股票跌跌撞撞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/s-p-500-tumbles-as-tariff-war-ignites-growth-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国股票周四下跌，删除了2万亿美元的价值，并将S＆amp; p 500指数送回更正领土，因为唐纳德·特朗普总统的严重新贸易关税激发了广泛的经济衰退恐惧，并留下了投资者寻求安全的债券和日历。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/s-p-500-tumbles-as-tariff-war-ignites-growth-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 13:44:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非股票在三年中大部分都在关税率高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/south-african-stocks-tumble-most-in-five-years-on-us-tariff-hit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非股票在三年来的最大幅度最高，因为该国出口的美国关税使公司利润和经济的看法云。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/south-african-stocks-tumble-most-in-five-years-on-us-tariff-hit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 13:42:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普给中国XI一个赢得关税打击世界的机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-gives-china-s-xi-a-chance-to-win-over-world-hit-by-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）提高对几乎每个国家的关税的决定将对中国经济造成打击。但这也是在XI赋予罕见的开放，以加深整体关系，包括与美国在亚洲及其他地区的关键盟友。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-gives-china-s-xi-a-chance-to-win-over-world-hit-by-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 12:20:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国和法国推动更积极的关税回应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/germany-and-france-push-for-a-more-aggressive-tariff-response</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国和德国正在推动对美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的关税措施做出更强有力的反应，并提倡有力的报复，这可以加强欧盟的谈判立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/germany-and-france-push-for-a-more-aggressive-tariff-response</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 10:52:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的关税威胁着全球经济，商品遭受重创</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/commodities-hit-as-trump-s-tariffs-threaten-demand-and-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于唐纳德·特朗普总统对猛烈抨击的猛烈抨击，石油从工业金属到谷物的其他商品跌至谷物，这造成了一场贸易战，威胁着损害全球经济和对原材料的需求。黄金从新鲜的纪录中落下。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/commodities-hit-as-trump-s-tariffs-threaten-demand-and-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 08:57:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>自八月以来，大多数欧洲股票因关税冲击而下沉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/european-stock-futures-decline-as-trump-tariffs-hurt-sentiment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）宣布了一个世纪以来最陡峭的关税，其中包括欧盟的20％的税率，欧洲股票遭受了八个月来最糟糕的一天。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/european-stock-futures-decline-as-trump-tariffs-hurt-sentiment</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 00:57:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当美国贸易战争颠覆全球前景时，市场抛售会加速</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/fear-grips-markets-as-trump-tariffs-raise-risks-to-global-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全世界，随着卖出订单在东京到伦敦和纽约的交易地板上照亮了屏幕，这是一个醒目的现实：唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）认真对待全球贸易体系＆Mdash＆Mdash;至少在目前看来，对股票市场崩溃的担忧并不能阻止他。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/fear-grips-markets-as-trump-tariffs-raise-risks-to-global-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 22:43:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当特朗普的关税达到价格大权时，汽车制造商闲置的植物，重新考虑价格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/trump-spares-automakers-from-more-pain-in-reciprocal-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[生效仅几个小时后，唐纳德·特朗普总统对进口汽车的25％关税已经在全球回荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/trump-spares-automakers-from-more-pain-in-reciprocal-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 22:09:33 GMT</pubDate>
